1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to appropriations; to appropriate funds to aid
2 in carrying out the provisions of Legislative Bill 1075, One Hundred
3 Ninth Legislature, Second Session, 2026; and to declare an
4 emergency.
5 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
-1-

LB1075A LB1075A
2026 2026
1 Section 1. There is hereby appropriated (1) $12,000 from the
2 Nebraska Accountability and Disclosure Commission Cash Fund for FY2025-26
3 and (2) $25,000 from the Nebraska Accountability and Disclosure
4 Commission Cash Fund for FY2026-27 to the Nebraska Accountability and
5 Disclosure Commission, for Program 94, to aid in carrying out the
6 provisions of Legislative Bill 1075, One Hundred Ninth Legislature,
7 Second Session, 2026.
8 No expenditures for permanent and temporary salaries and per diems
9 for state employees shall be made from funds appropriated in this
10 section.
11 Sec. 2. Since an emergency exists, this act takes effect when
12 passed and approved according to law.
